# ğŸ›¡ï¸ Secure Static Website Hosting on AWS

This project securely hosts a static website on AWS using the following services:
- **Amazon S3** for static site hosting
- **CloudFront** for global content delivery
- **AWS Certificate Manager (ACM)** for HTTPS
- **AWS WAF** for protection against common web exploits


ğŸ” Security Best Practices Followed

âŒ No root account access (IAM used instead)

âœ… MFA enabled for all IAM users

âœ… S3 access logging enabled

âœ… CloudFront enforces HTTPS

âœ… WAF blocks XSS, SQLi, and bad bots

âœ… Least privilege IAM policy for users

 
